                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable</hi> 257.) I produce a certi<lb></lb>ficate of the prisoner's former conviction at Kingstom—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 19th Oct.</hi> 1841<hi rend="italic">and confined twelve month</hi>)—the prisoner is the man.</p>
